---
description: Backend control-plane service rules.
globs:
  - "services/**"
  - "migrations/**"
  - "infra/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Backend

- Do: store only ephemeral presence, anti-abuse, and minimal metadata by default.
- Do: use parameterized SQL, migrations, timeouts, cancellation, bounded retries.
- Do: keep sealed mailbox disabled by default; ciphertext only when enabled.
- Never: persist ordinary profile bodies, photos, or message plaintext.
- Never: apply production Terraform from an autonomous agent session.
- Verify: `make test-integration` and migration checks for schema changes.
